message: "If you use or refer to this software, please cite it as below."
title: "Aurora-Lens Demo: Evidence Authority and Runtime Admissibility Governance"
type: software

authors:
  - family-names: "Stokes"
    given-names: "Margaret"
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0009-0004-6422-4174"

abstract: >
  Aurora-Lens Demo is a bounded, runnable demonstration of runtime admissibility
  governance for AI outputs. It demonstrates evidence authority demotion,
  freshness-aware decision blocking, and audit-record generation before model
  output becomes consequential.

keywords:
  - AI governance
  - admissibility
  - runtime governance
  - evidence authority
  - audit ledger
  - LLM governance
  - Aurora-Lens

